        <tag>博客搭建</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>fancybox图片预览</title>
    <url>/blog/2020/11/29/fancybox%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E9%A2%84%E8%A7%88/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>优化博客小技巧</p>
<h2 id="从GitHub克隆fancybox"><a href="#从GitHub克隆fancybox" class="headerlink" title="从GitHub克隆fancybox"></a>从GitHub克隆fancybox</h2><p>打开cmd,进入到个人博客文件夹的themes/next/source/lib</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/theme-next/theme-next-fancybox3 fancybox</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>git clone –git克隆命令<br>url –GitHub里的fancybox文件路径<br>fancybox –定义克隆后的文件名<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/hdy-commin/pic@main/img/9.png" width="300px"></p>
<h2 id="打开主题配置文件next-config-yml"><a href="#打开主题配置文件next-config-yml" class="headerlink" title="打开主题配置文件next/_config.yml"></a>打开主题配置文件next/_config.yml</h2><p>配置fancybox是否应用</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">fancybox: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/hdy-commin/pic@main/img/10.png" width="300px">
## 测试效果

<p> 进入博客，点击图片<br> <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/hdy-commin/pic@main/img/3.png" width="300px"><br> 实现了放大艺兴哥的帅照</p>
<h2 id="结语"><a href="#结语" class="headerlink" title="结语"></a>结语</h2><blockquote>
<p>博客小白，不足很多<br>如有侵权，联系必删<br>生命不息，优化不止<br>Author: Daiyin</p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
